info.description: The purpose of this application is to provide process services to consult the catalog of icorebanking vi crediboard definitions.
info.title: Icorebanking Vi Crediboard Query Process Service API

get.description: The purpose of this service is to measure the current percentage of a concept for the approval of a credit application.
get.summary: Set measure rate of approval instance decisions

get.description: Returns the information of the posted obligations of a prospectus.
get.summary: Query the booked obligations of a prospectus

get.description: The obligation entity for credit application is consulted taking into account the number of the credit application. (k_tipodr and k_numdoc)
get.summary: Consult the obligation by credit request

get.description:
* Process service that implements the consultation of the users who have the necessary role to execute a credit request. The roles are directly related to the positions, for this reason the positions that have the assigned role must be consulted and then the users who perform said positions.
* A query is made in the business rule for this entity, in case of not returning data, it returns the possible users who are registered in the Database.
get.summary: Return all users who have a given role or load
Consult the processing error by id

get.description:
Consultation process service that allows you to consult a credit request in process using a token...
This service returns requests that are in process or that take 30 days or less to complete.
get.summary: Consult a credit request in process using a token

get.description:
Search for all credit requests (from prospects). assigned to the user making the query. This service takes the {X-User-Name} as the querying officer.
This service returns requests that are in process or that take 30 days or less to complete.
get.summary: Search for all credit requests (from prospects). assigned to the user making the query.

get.description:
Search for all credit applications (prospects) without assigning them to an officer.
This service returns requests that are in process or that take 30 days or less to complete.
get.summary: Search for all credit applications (prospects) without assigning them to an officer.

get.description:
Implement the consultation process service that allows you to consult the relevant data of the credit requests in process...
This service returns requests that are in process or that take 30 days or less to complete.
get.summary: Consult the relevant data of the credit requests in process

X-Total-Count.description: Total records found in the query

get.description:
Consultation process service that allows you to consult a credit request in process by its identifier...
This service returns requests that are in process or that take 30 days or less to complete.
get.summary: Consult a credit request in process by its identifier

get.description: * Process service that implements the consultation only of credit applications (of prospects) that have registered news without reading.
get.summary: Return all credit applications (from prospects). who have news registered without reading.

X-Total-Count.description: Total records found in the query

get.summary: Consult the money destinations by id

X-Total-Count.description: Total records found in the query
